graph TB
    subgraph "TrustyAI Service Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager]
        Webhook[Conversion Webhook Server]
        MetricsProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Metrics Protection]

        Controller -->|serves| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| MetricsProxy
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        TrustyAICR[TrustyAIService CR<br/>v1/v1alpha1]
        LMEvalCR[LMEvalJob CR<br/>v1alpha1]
        GuardrailsCR[GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Services"
        TrustyAIService[TrustyAI Service<br/>Explainability & Bias Detection]
        LMEvalJob[LM Eval Job<br/>Language Model Evaluation]
        GuardrailsOrch[Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>AI Safety & Content Filtering]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecars<br/>OpenShift Authentication]
    end

    subgraph "Resources Created"
        Deployments[Deployments]
        Services[Services]
        Routes[OpenShift Routes]
        VirtualServices[Istio VirtualServices]
        ServiceMonitors[ServiceMonitors<br/>Prometheus]
        Secrets[TLS Secrets<br/>service-ca]
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| TrustyAICR
    User -->|creates| LMEvalCR
    User -->|creates| GuardrailsCR

    TrustyAICR -->|watched by| Controller
    LMEvalCR -->|watched by| Controller
    GuardrailsCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| TrustyAIService
    Controller -->|creates/manages| LMEvalJob
    Controller -->|creates/manages| GuardrailsOrch
    Controller -->|creates/manages| OAuthProxy

    Controller -->|creates| Deployments
    Controller -->|creates| Services
    Controller -->|creates| Routes
    Controller -->|creates| VirtualServices
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceMonitors
    Controller -->|creates| Secrets

    TrustyAIService -->|uses| OAuthProxy
    GuardrailsOrch -->|uses| OAuthProxy

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|watches/patches| KServe[KServe InferenceService]
    Controller -->|configures| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    TrustyAIService -->|monitors| KServe
    GuardrailsOrch -->|calls| KServe
    LMEvalJob -->|evaluates| KServe

    %% Storage
    TrustyAIService -->|persists to| Storage[PVC or PostgreSQL/MySQL]
    LMEvalJob -->|stores results| S3[S3-compatible Storage]

    %% Workload Management
    LMEvalJob -->|managed by| Kueue[Kueue Workload Queue]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes via| ServiceMonitors

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style TrustyAICR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style LMEvalCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style GuardrailsCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style TrustyAIService fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style LMEvalJob fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style GuardrailsOrch fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServe fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ModelMesh fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Storage fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Kueue fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333
